    "body": "## State synchronized\n\n- records repair integration main SHA `47ed2df0908d82da91b14b9cb85ff01f0bf1f12c` and PR #228;\n- advances repository and live Drive memory revision to `2026-07-17-0123-JST`;\n- distinguishes repository plugin 1.0.14 from the still-installed local plugin 1.0.13;\n- records local installation, manifest parity, and real Slot 1 mutation canary as pending;\n- preserves the user pause and Stage 6 pause;\n- closes the repair task as integrated while keeping installation and live acceptance explicitly open.\n\nDocumentation and memory only. No runtime, gameplay, bridge mailbox, plugin implementation, or Stage 6 files change.",
